      "explanation": "Solve for length at the lowest tone (20 Hz).",
      "notations": "L₍min₎ = v / (2 f₍min₎) = 343 / (40) ≈ 8.6 m"
    },
    {
      "explanation": "Similarly find the length for the highest fundamental (20 kHz).",
      "notations": "L₍max freq₎ = v / (2 f₍max₎) = 343 / (4.0 × 10⁴) ≈ 8.6 × 10⁻³ m"
    },
    {
      "explanation": "Thus pipes ranging from ≈8.6 m down to ≈8.6 mm cover the audible band.",
